'''''Nuages du Monde''''' is an album by  new age/electronic music group  in 2006 (see ).
The title is French, and translates to "Clouds of the World".
"Angelicus", the lead single, was released only as a  in 2007; [http://www.discogs.com/release/881026] Its release to DJs enabled the track to reach number one on the U.S.  chart during the week ending , . A music video was also filmed and released, despite the lack of a commercial single release.
The second single, "Lost and Found", was also promotional and was released later in 2007.[http://www.discogs.com/release/993739] It has reached number four on the Hot Dance Club Play chart as of the week ending , .